high_descs: Walk across the room and face the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the cup on the counter.
Step to the left and face the shelves on the wall.
Place the cup in the middle on the second shelf from the top.
Turn right and walk across the room, then turn right and walk to the end of the counter and turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the glass on the end of the counter.
Turn left and walk across the room, then turn left and walk across the room and turn right to face the shelves.
Place the glass on the right of the first glass.
anns.task_desc: To move two glass to the second shelf from the top of the shelves.

high_descs: Walk and stand in front of the paper towels that are to the left of the stove in front of you.
Pick up the cup that's above the paper towels.
Turn around and walk to the counter then turn right and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the shelves.
Put the cup to the left of the salt shaker on the top shelf.
Turn right and walk to the sink then turn right and walk to the toaster that;s on your left and face it when you get to it.
Pick up the glass that;s by the toaster.
Go back to where you put the first glass.
Put this glass to the right of the first.
anns.task_desc: Put two glasses on the shelf.

high_descs: Proceed to counter, turn right.  Turn left once reach cabinet next to stove.  Turn left.
Pick up glass from behind paper towels.
Turn left and proceed to wall.  Turn left to face shelf.
Place glass on third shelf up, to the right of the sponge, directly in front of left shaker.
Turn right, proceed to sink.  Turn right, proceed to end of left counter.  Turn left to face counter.
Pick up glass in front and to the right of the toaster.
Turn left, proceed to counter, turn left, proceed to wall.  Turn right to face shelf.
Put glass directly to right of first glass, directly in front of the white shaker.
anns.task_desc: Move two glasses to a shelf.
